  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription -> We have discovered the site of an ancient block ruins, where the streets were once lined with shops. The map also indicates the presence of an entrance to an underground commercial street, promising the discovery of numerous high-value items..</li>
  -->
  <AM_Quest_Street.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings><li>questDescription -> 我們發現了一個遠古街區遺址，那里的街道曾經擠滿了商店。地圖上還顯示那里有一條地下商業街的入口，有望發現許多高價值的物品。</li></AM_Quest_Street.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
